      <title>中国潜伏之际，美国与萨尔瓦多总统布克莱重修旧好</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-mends-fences-with-el-salvadors-bukele-china-lurks-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前，萨尔瓦多总统纳伊布·布克莱(Nayib Bukele)在WhatsApp上发布了与美国驻这个中美洲国家最高外交官的私人对话，他传达了自己的信息：我不会听从美国的命令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-mends-fences-with-el-salvadors-bukele-china-lurks-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国因边境冲突召见缅甸特使</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-summons-myanmar-envoy-over-border-clashes-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国周二召见邻国缅甸大使，抗议随着缅甸叛军与其军政府政权之间的战斗加剧，边境暴力不断升级，孟加拉国一侧造成两人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bangladesh-summons-myanmar-envoy-over-border-clashes-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 15:14:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自称比特币发明者否认伪造文件来支持其主张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-denies-forging-documents-support-claim-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位自称发明了比特币的澳大利亚计算机科学家周二告诉伦敦一家法院，他从未伪造文件来试图证明他备受争议的主张，因为他在一场关于加密货币所有权的法律斗争中开始提供证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/self-proclaimed-bitcoin-inventor-denies-forging-documents-support-claim-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 13:53:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年巴基斯坦选举：关键问题是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/despite-multiple-crises-pakistan-elections-dominated-by-personalities-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦周四举行大选，上届全国大选获胜者、受欢迎的前总理伊姆兰·汗被监禁，尽管经济危机和其他问题威胁着这个拥有核武器的国家，但他仍占据头条新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/despite-multiple-crises-pakistan-elections-dominated-by-personalities-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 11:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电拟建日本第二家芯片工厂 投资额达200亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-build-second-japan-chip-factory-raising-investment-20-bln-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾芯片制造商台积电周二表示，将在日本建造第二家工厂，并于 2027 年底投入运营，在东京政府的支持下，其日本合资企业的总投资将超过 200 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-build-second-japan-chip-factory-raising-investment-20-bln-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:51:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024年巴基斯坦大选：新政府将面临哪些挑战？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/multiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦将于周四举行全国选举，选出新政府，多重危机困扰着这个拥有 2.41 亿人口的拥有核武器的南亚国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/multiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年巴基斯坦选举：如何进行？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-do-national-elections-pakistan-work-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦周四将举行广受关注的全国选举，选举将组建新政府，在未来五年内领导这个饱受危机困扰的南亚国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-do-national-elections-pakistan-work-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:28:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦总统任命办公厅主任贝克特诺夫为新总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kazakh-president-names-chief-staff-bektenov-new-pm-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦总统卡西姆-乔马尔特·托卡耶夫周二任命其幕僚长奥尔扎斯·别克捷诺夫为总理，很快就获得了执政党阿马纳特党主导的议会的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kazakh-president-names-chief-staff-bektenov-new-pm-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 09:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国海警船进入东海争议海域</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警表示，周二在钓鱼岛海域进行了巡逻。钓鱼岛是中国、日本和台湾都声称拥有主权的东海领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
