      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/telkom-indonesia-looking-sell-stake-data-centre-business-conclude-deal-by-h2-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼国有通信巨头Telkom Indonesia正在考虑出售其数据中心业务的股份，预计将在今年下半年完成出售流程。]]></description>
